{"type": "article", "id": 25214, "title": "遇到这 22 种情况，我只想说我已经尽力了 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "不要哈哈哈哈哈哈！那会让人感到更心酸！", "date": "2016-04-10T07:00:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 255, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130328mns4HQBXb3DR1ahW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">好奇心研究所的微博（<a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1006065587974982\" target=\"_blank\">@好奇心研究所</a>）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。  <b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 劝傻逼。@ Asteriskerix    </b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130310HdtuPYxfsXi3INTG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2. 被傻逼劝。@张扬\r\n\r\n</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130311SEKkX5iG67NaylUO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56066946\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 五音不全，唱 KTV。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130312Yl4vRotWwBGsuHcM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 从小手残，画眼线。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130313Bcaf3vxGOHCMb6Lz.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 就不信做不了糖醋排骨，查菜谱，问老妈，200 块买食材，烧出一盘黑炭。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130313CsJby8ZROm04BEqc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 思考一个月，参考海量街拍，跟理发师沟通一小时，在镜子里看见新发型。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130314iaAtkQ4h3HCInEfS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 睡前犹豫 20 分钟定六点半还是六点四十五，咬咬牙定了六点半，第二天 12 点才起来。 </b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130315325vPjONfWwxJS9c.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 一星期不吃晚饭，哭着搂着胃睡去，上称掉了 0.1 斤。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130315rqjyz2vKZQwNpDVE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56571429\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>9. 11 点上床躺着不玩手机，4 点半眼睛瞪得像铜铃。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130316xYhZBugAbNjfsyRc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>10. 满 79 免运费，买了 70。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021303170yh9ivHW3Fu7ZALX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75555556\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 在北京开车，一个小时开出 500 米。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130318Hm8rWw9t2Lv61QRd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21527778\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 在香港租房子。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021303196rmwQTn4u1YeIaHA.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 早上蹲厕所。@miss      <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130319bfcV2ujaNGvwYRIS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 秒射…@  kevin哥<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021303204pQ0LTRDBHZOGcYv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.068\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><b>15. 脱单。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130321bqnE4jQUkWZclsw2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>16. KPI。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213032187UYEczjkXs42Z6H.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75347222\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>17. 猪队友。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130322BWrQgR3pNLUSEjeV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>18. 老板说了一个笑话。/ 跟老板说一个笑话。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021303232Awkz8isPnCl6qZW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>19. 长成这样。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130324yHlZiYhew6rmXDba.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.024\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>20. 学立体几何的时候。教立体几何的时候。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130325YmfTNxS47iBtRKvq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>21. 考完试，听见同学对答案。 @甬道<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130326RnQgFtGCYlVpqKax.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.508\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>22. 带娃。跟婆婆一起带娃。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213032668IihLq3efsPobjB.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56338028\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em>  <br></p>\n\n\n"}